<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>النَّاسُ فِيمَا يَعْشَقُونَ مَذَاهِبُ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c3">{أَبُو فِرَاسٍ الحَمَدَانيّ}</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
